Package: marge
Title: API for HOMER in R for Genomic Analysis using Tidy Conventions
Version: 0.0.4.9999
Authors@R: c(
  person("Robert A.", "Amezquita", , "robert.amezquita@fredhutch.org", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
  )		   
Description: API for HOMER in R for genomic analysis using tidy conventions. Runs HOMER from native R functions and allows for organization of motif enrichment analysis, and subsequent reading in of motifs into tidily formatted tibbles for further analysis and visualization of many parallel analyses.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
